    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Austrian unit of currency 1925-2002, with a lapse during WWII. It was replaced by the Euro as the country’s sole currency in 2002. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
